original_name: Trailer Park Boys: Out of the Park: USA
overview: The boys are back on the loose as Bubbles, Julian and Ricky head south of the Canadian border for some outrageous American adventures.

episodes.name: Orlando 1
episodes.overview: After finding out that Bubs misread the fine print about their hotel situation, the Boys head to the astronaut training program at NASA.

episodes.name: Orlando 2
episodes.overview: Still in Orlando, Bubbles and the Boys go to a big cat park. Ricky attempts to wrestle an alligator and Julian takes the Boys off-roading.

episodes.name: Charlotte
episodes.overview: Still in Orlando, Bubbles and the Boys go to a big cat park. Ricky attempts to wrestle an alligator and Julian takes the Boys off-roading.

episodes.name: New Orleans
episodes.overview: In New Orleans, the Boys take on a giant pile of seafood, Julian visits a psychic, Ricky looks for a doctor, and Bubs sleeps in a cemetery.

episodes.name: Memphis
episodes.overview: Ricky has an unfortunate accident when the Boys get to Memphis. Then, they meet Rush guitarist Alex Lifeson, who helps Bubbles record a song.

episodes.name: Nashville
episodes.overview: The Boys arrive in Nashville. Bubbles shops for a suit to wear in his new music video, while Ricky and Julian look for a car and some girls.

episodes.name: Los Angeles 1
episodes.overview: Ricky gets into a pot-smoking competition with "Anthony Stoner" in LA. Later, the Boys try to play basketball to win some money.

episodes.name: Los Angeles 2
episodes.overview: The Boys wrap up the trip in LA as they finally shoot the music video with the help of famous friends Sebastian Bach, Tom Green and Verne Troyer.
